reviewText: The film was delieved very promptly.  It was excellent quality considering the age of the film.
The person I bought this for absolutely adored it: watched it 5 times the first time they got it. I guess it's a classic in the Traditional Mexican Family.
She is old favorite of my mother. I grew up watching my mom gloved this movie she has watched over ans over.

This movie brought back old memories from when my Dad would take us to the spanish theatre.
My sisters and I loved it!!
